PlastoGram identifies subchloroplast localisation of proteins using random forests with n-gram encoding and profile hidden Markov models

Restrictions: * Be patient - calculations can take up to few minutes. * Up to 50 sequences may be analyzed at the same time using web server. If you need larger query, please use the PlastoGram package for R. * Make sure to provide sequences in FASTA format with amino acids in uppercase letters.
